  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Thread natto, garlic, and ful medames onto skewers.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together miso paste, lemon juice, and olive oil.",
    "Brush the miso mixture onto the skewers.",
    "Season with sumac, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bake the skewers for 15 minutes or until the natto is molten.",
    "Serve the skewers with low-glycemic pita bread.",
    "Drizzle with additional miso mixture if desired.",
    "Let cool for a few minutes before serving."
